{"tid":270112,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"[ukulele]新手唔識睇點掃弦","createTime":"2017-06-04T06:25:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-06T10:56:23.000Z","uid":114181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6ee8af248de8342a60a9786d74e4186e16c7db3f","tid":270112,"uid":114181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T06:25:43.000Z","msg":"之前上過堂，但發現跟唔上進度，而家會係屋企自己練，有d基本問題唔識<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://yoopu.me/view/o%3Arp8y6k1L\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoopu.me%2Fview%2Fo%253Arp8y6k1L&d=vBAjQ5xdjjLSHqkih4VZf%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=b62d2ccb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://yoopu.me/view/o%3Arp8y6k1L</a><br />\n<br />\n上面譜既節奏其實點睇呢？搞唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同期一齊學嘅朋友已放棄，希望搵到同道中人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6e36087de9bce4a51104192324c3859464fa2da","tid":270112,"uid":357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T17:45:15.000Z","msg":"X係嗰下彈邊條線<br />\n拍子係 1拍，半拍，半拍，總共一小節兩拍<br />\n唔知點講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e8bc044f6c634edd2bb55a409037ecdfa0f6457","tid":270112,"uid":97826,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T18:02:40.000Z","msg":"佢果度意思係有兩種方法去做個節奏<br />\n你首先跟住拍子數<br />\n1 &amp; 2 &amp; 3 &amp; 4 &amp;<br />\n<br />\n第一種就係 1時掃一下個chord<br />\n然後 2 同 &amp; 就分别彈第三同第四條弦 (當然係hold 住個chord)<br />\n而右手應該用 中指 同無名 (就當佢叫佢 2號同3號手指)黎彈第3同4條弦<br />\n<br />\n咁彈法即係<br />\n1  &amp;  2  &amp;  3  &amp;  4  &amp; | 1 &amp;  2  &amp;  3  &amp;  4  &amp;<br />\n掃     2  3  掃     2  3   掃     2  3  掃     2  3<br />\n<br />\n第二種就同第一種差唔多，只係果下掃chord用同時三條弦代替 (即係拇指 中指 無名指)，然後果兩下單音係用食指同中指<br />\n<br />\n1  &amp;  2  &amp;  3  &amp;  4  &amp; <br />\nT      1  2   T      1  2<br />\n2               2<br />\n3               3"},{"pid":"fda6019e4471f4f354ea3eb5bf41ff53727a8616","tid":270112,"uid":97826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T18:03:17.000Z","msg":"打完出黎走哂位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65e7c4f6fdacf3d3b37c7e5badc89d4a474d1892","tid":270112,"uid":97826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T18:12:07.000Z","msg":"其實最簡單就係1 2 3 4咁逐下掃<br />\n掃弦+勾弦既協調冇咁快上到手<br />\n<br />\n寧願你轉chord順同快先<br />\n因為淨掃chord都可以有好多變化"},{"pid":"fb945829386238425ae357b28cb501d0400ac3ae","tid":270112,"uid":97826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T18:14:11.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47686dcb293468f20f1e6c9106720dd5fb31899e","tid":270112,"uid":114181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T23:42:19.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n放假再試下"},{"pid":"5079149bb62d82d66c90b6f743cbadc0f1b33ac5","tid":270112,"uid":97826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T03:05:30.000Z","msg":"有唔明再問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faea7e0b2a76b92a305a6162d6395ade93223b47","tid":270112,"uid":87925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:06:39.000Z","msg":"巴打加油，我都剛剛學 UKULELE，仲掃緊 C Am F G <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abc08594c16a5b408d7f5bb2584d30bfdb2508b6","tid":270112,"uid":114181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T10:56:23.000Z","msg":"我係絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n加油巴打<br />\n<br />\n幾好玩其實"}]}